                                    <note>16 salām. The text ends abruptly after the 16th salām for Ṗagʷǝmen, belonging to the 6th of this month, which is the 
                                        last but one according to the edition of <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebautGuidi1913Synaxaire"/>
                                            <citedRange unit="page">472</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                                    <explicit xml:lang="gez">ሰይከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ጸሪቀ፡ መበለት፡ ውኩፈ። እምእለ፡ አብኡ፡ ብዑላን፡ ተርፈ።</explicit>
